<h4>Which language is the best?</h4>
<p>
    There is no "best" language. All languages have their pros/cons and may be more suitable in certain situations. We cover
    a variety of languages in our program to teach several in-demand languages and expose students to different language syntax and programs.
    After learning the concepts of these languages, students will have the skills to learn and use other languages without too much difficulty.
</p>
